> these pdf's backed up offline and would you be willing to upload
them
> to a new folder in the files section?
>

>

Whoops! This is my fault, I think I must have changed that access
permissions on my files on the server accidently when I was updating
some of the files. It has probably been like this for a few months
since it has been quite a while since I've touched my site.
I need to change webhosts anyway so I will soon fix this up. The new
address will be: http://quikscript.heliohost.org/ (I think). I will
post a message when I've fixed this up (I might be a few days though--
sorry )
